Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉  温泉  温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔  这么喜欢温泉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起进去的大浴池…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.43,0:00:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比乃乃香家里的浴池还要大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比湖还要大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没那么离谱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:00:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽中的话就可以亲自去确认一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉  温泉  温泉  温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.95,0:01:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:03:02.74,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,460)\pos(32,270)}「真正的朋友」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个你看  也很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不想要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你  头奖产生了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  原来是凑太啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少见啊  柚季居然在家帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不像凑太  特地跑到别的店里去帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受人所托  那也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受小春所托  那也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要做留学的准备  今天是最后一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才旅馆的女主人来过  说可以去玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔泡个温泉也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有凑太的份呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能跟我们一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想和你们一起去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会跟妹妹什么的一起去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  既然有了结论
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在店里会妨碍到别人  请你出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春  有件事想拜托一下你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也没有变化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音  呐  看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  温泉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  碰巧从熟人那里拿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个熟人说  一定要邀请乃乃香一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从谁那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应别人不能说的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受陌生人给的东西好像不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  才不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一个你稍微想想就能知道的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周末  等着你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的住宿券  怎么办好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  柚季  去不去泡温泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉？  正好超想去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住宿券  还有多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.97,0:06:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得正是时候  温泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  听我说听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去泡温泉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是汐音邀请我去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个休息日  一起去泡温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  玩得开心点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我看一下店
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:06:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  诺艾尔不能来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多出来的券怎么办  问问小春吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看她有没有别的想邀请的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的话三个人也可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  多出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也挺忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  是小春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  下个周末  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  是有空
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰箱里面还有些咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃的话  加热后再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得用小火  不然容易糊掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸自己也能做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.32,0:08:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是这样  也要记得吃些沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你总是挑食
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  吃完咖喱的碟子别直接放着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然之后会很难清洗的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差不多该出发了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经这个时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  让爸爸一个人留在家里  我有点担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她差不多快到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比预期的要早到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些话想和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不早了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再慢点过来也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  下次我会来得晚些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  今天不是休息日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店里的工作没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店铺的话  没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经找到人手了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也有卖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手伸得够长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:09:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然味道是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是绝对是小时候的好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是美味依旧  椎原家的飞碟馒头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是露天的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  请享用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉  温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和汐音一起去温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景色不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  柚季竟然会这样评价
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.77,0:11:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我才没有认同飞碟的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是在休战中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.09,0:11:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下等下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你们还在这里优哉游哉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝茶之前  我们有其他事情要做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到了温泉  就应该去泡温泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们来得太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想…去泡温泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季  你这样好么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在这里玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有话想和乃乃香说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:11:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回房间了  你要好好加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  我有话想和你说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}好  好  干
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}我  知  道  了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠军就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  你想和我说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会再说也可以  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}冠军就是你  冠军就是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以  也可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  贴纸掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔要玩这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,300)\1cAD5656\bord0\frz10}计\N数\N器\N故\N障\N中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这机子似乎坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我不想再绕圈子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下  柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音  快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的样子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次应该能说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是我拜托了小春
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀请乃乃香过来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为怎么想都觉得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处在于平日不同的地方的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.21,0:13:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许就能将难以启齿的话说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  我听你说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.19,0:14:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直留在心中挥之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对乃乃香做过那些过分的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果这样就可以原谅我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请你随意打我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你尽全力的打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  那我打了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预  备…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了用全力么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话不就变得不公平了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这样就算打平了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年我就不在这个小镇了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀请我的话也是可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然只有那一晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  可以吃掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太想吃  都给你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音喜欢飞碟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你一直在拍飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍照  是为了更深入地了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃点心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去泡茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干…干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  果然是柚季啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为摘了眼镜  看不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是认错人怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  那件事怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能被邀请来  真是太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托二位的福了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次把诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及户川同学都一起叫来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是浑身清爽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去喝点什么冷饮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱掉  脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这全都是浴池？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点下水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起洗真是愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡就是洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和别人一起又如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人暖洋洋的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是这是给凑太发的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为让他帮了店里的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有想让他一起来什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  乃乃香心中有没有装着什么人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真没劲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡觉睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从何时开始  不再是孤单一人的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.73,0:19:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还醒着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  明明在我家买就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  给爸爸和…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妈妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个能干的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  下次可以去乃乃香家里玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  随时欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.18,0:19:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉真大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒觉得很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩得真是愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为和朋友在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔和汐音是好朋友  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别擅自决定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友什么的  我已经不想再交第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  你喜欢飞碟对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西…怎么可能抱着走在大街上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真的是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱汤？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试着做了做  尝尝看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  不先把之前剩下的吃掉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.42,0:21:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么生气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都告诉过你不要弄糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得比起放在我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是放在这里更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.11,0:21:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事…想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:21:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖洋洋
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
